1232
02:22:27,660 --> 02:22:32,090
他是个非常机灵的小男孩 总有一天他会成为了不起的皇帝的
He's a very clever little boy. He'll make a grand emperor one day.

1233
02:22:33,540 --> 02:22:36,040
我们在读伟大的安东尼
We've been reading about the great Mark Antony,

1234
02:22:36,040 --> 02:22:37,460
和他在埃及的冒险
and his adventures in Egypt.

1235
02:22:37,460 --> 02:22:40,090
还有皇后用蛇自杀的故事
And the queen killed herself with a snake.

1236
02:22:40,090 --> 02:22:43,510
我还没告诉你发生在我们祖先身上的故事
And just wait until you hear what happened to our ancestors.

1237
02:22:43,510 --> 02:22:45,420
如果你很乖的话
If you're very good,

1238
02:22:45,430 --> 02:22:49,300
明晚我会给你讲克劳迪亚斯皇帝的故事
tomorrow night, I'll tell you the story of Emperor Claudius.

1239
02:22:49,300 --> 02:22:51,110
他身边最亲近的人
He was betrayed

1240
02:22:52,220 --> 02:22:54,450
背叛了他
by those closest to him.

1241
02:22:56,230 --> 02:22:58,080
他的亲人
By his own blood.

1242
02:22:59,310 --> 02:23:01,860
他们在黑暗的角落里商议
They whispered in dark corners

1243
02:23:01,860 --> 02:23:04,400
并且在半夜偷偷出去
and went out late at night,

1244
02:23:04,400 --> 02:23:07,840
共同密谋
and conspired, and conspired.

1245
02:23:10,370 --> 02:23:14,300
但皇帝知道他们在策划阴谋
But the Emperor Claudius knew that they were up to something.

1246
02:23:14,330 --> 02:23:16,970
他知道他们像小蜜蜂一样忙碌
He knew they were busy little bees.

1247
02:23:18,830 --> 02:23:21,980
有天晚上 他和其中一人谈话
And one night he sat down with one of them,

1248
02:23:22,670 --> 02:23:24,770
他看着她
and he looked at her,

1249
02:23:25,420 --> 02:23:27,070
然后说
and he said,

1250
02:23:28,130 --> 02:23:30,820
"告诉我你们的计划
"Tell me what you've been doing,

1251
02:23:31,390 --> 02:23:33,200
忙碌的小蜜蜂
"busy little bee.

1252
02:23:35,390 --> 02:23:38,580
不然我会杀死你最亲的人
"Or I shall strike down those dearest to you.

1253
02:23:39,650 --> 02:23:42,790
你会看到我身上沾满他们的鲜血"
"You shall watch as I bathe in their blood."

1254
02:23:46,400 --> 02:23:48,920
而皇帝的心都碎了
And the Emperor was heartbroken.

1255
02:23:50,910 --> 02:23:53,200
小蜜蜂对他的伤害
The little bee had wounded him more deeply

1256
02:23:53,200 --> 02:23:56,010
比任何人都要深
than anyone else could ever have done.

1257
02:23:58,040 --> 02:24:01,020
卢修斯 你认为接下来会发生什么事
What do you think happened then, Lucius?

1258
02:24:01,540 --> 02:24:03,480
我不知道 舅舅
I don't know, Uncle.

1259
02:24:09,880 --> 02:24:12,570
小蜜蜂告诉了他所有的事
The little bee told him everything.

1260
02:25:10,360 --> 02:25:13,460
开闸 皇上有令
Open, in the name of the Emperor!

1261
