Move! Form a column on the left!

1275
02:26:15,390 --> 02:26:18,680
我只需要机会脱身 千万别做无谓的牺牲
I only need moments, so do not be careless with your lives.

1276
02:26:18,680 --> 02:26:21,220
不想被卷入这事的 就回到囚室里去
If you don't want any part of this, go back to your cells.

1277
02:26:21,220 --> 02:26:23,560
我们会留在这里帮你 马西墨斯
We'll wait here for you, Maximus.

1278
02:26:23,560 --> 02:26:25,440
- 勇气和荣誉 - 勇气和荣誉
- Strength and honor. - Strength and honor.

1279
02:26:25,440 --> 02:26:26,580
去吧
Go.

1280
02:26:27,360 --> 02:26:29,290
勇气和荣誉
Strength and honor.

1281
02:26:31,820 --> 02:26:34,750
瞄准 拉弓
Aim. Arch your bows!

