02:27:30,240 --> 02:27:31,400
普罗西莫

1284
02:27:41,760 --> 02:27:43,160
一切终归尘土
Shadows and dust.

1285
02:28:24,970 --> 02:28:26,320
马西墨斯
Maximus!

1286
02:28:31,690 --> 02:28:33,210
对不起
I'm sorry.

1287
02:28:59,510 --> 02:29:00,980
事情都解决了
It's done.

1288
02:29:07,850 --> 02:29:09,820
该如何处治我的外甥
And what of my nephew?

1289
02:29:10,810 --> 02:29:12,910
还有他的母亲
And what of his mother?

1290
02:29:14,900 --> 02:29:17,540
他们应该面对和她爱人相同的命运吗
Should they share her lover's fate?

1291
02:29:19,150 --> 02:29:21,290
还是我应该网开一面
Or should I be merciful?

1292
02:29:23,910 --> 02:29:25,920
仁慈的康莫德斯
Commodus the Merciful.

1293
02:29:32,250 --> 02:29:34,680
从现在起 卢修斯由我照顾
Lucius will stay with me now.

1294
02:29:35,750 --> 02:29:37,640
如果他母亲
And if his mother

1295
02:29:38,920 --> 02:29:41,150
用令我不快的眼神看着我
so much as looks at me

1296
02:29:42,220 --> 02:29:44,820
用令我不快的态度对我
in a manner that displeases me,

1297
02:29:46,680 --> 02:29:48,200
他就会死
he will die.

1298
02:29:51,600 --> 02:29:54,950
如果她想 抵死不从
If she decides to be noble,

1299
02:29:56,610 --> 02:29:58,790
或者想自杀的话
and takes her own life,

1300
02:30:00,280 --> 02:30:01,840
他会死
he will die.

1301
02:30:05,360 --> 02:30:07,170
至于你
And as for you,

1302
02:30:09,870 --> 02:30:11,720
你会爱我
you will love me,

1303
02:30:12,460 --> 02:30:14,350
就像我爱你一样
as I have loved you.

1304
02:30:15,830 --> 02:30:19,600
你会帮我生育下一代 血统纯正的继承人
You will provide me with an heir of pure blood,

1305
02:30:20,460 --> 02:30:22,400
那么康莫德斯
so that Commodus

1306
02:30:22,880 --> 02:30:25,940
和他的子孙 将世世代代统治罗马
and his progeny will rule for 1, 000 years.

1307
02:30:30,470 --> 02:30:32,320
我不够仁慈吗
Am I not merciful?

1308
02:30:54,080 --> 02:30:56,810
我不够仁慈吗
Am I not merciful!

1309
02:31:08,930 --> 02:31:13,030
- 马西墨斯 马西墨斯 马西墨斯 - 马西墨斯 马西墨斯 马西墨斯
- Maximus! Maximus! Maximus! - Maximus! Maximus! Maximus!

1310
02:31:40,380 --> 02:31:43,230
我是军人 我职责是服从
I'm a soldier. I obey.

1311
02:31:45,880 --> 02:31:50,240
没人可以逼你做你不愿意的事
Nothing happens to anyone that he is not fitted by nature to bear.

1312
02:32:23,090 --> 02:32:29,150
马西墨斯
Maximus.

1313
02:32:30,760 --> 02:32:32,690
他们在为你欢呼
They call for you.

1314
02:32:34,560 --> 02:32:37,910
一个沦为奴隶的将军
The general who became a slave.

1315
02:32:39,060 --> 02:32:41,540
一个变成角斗士的奴隶
The slave who became a gladiator.

1316
02:32:42,810 --> 02:32:45,710
一个挑战皇帝的角斗士
The gladiator who defied an emperor.

1317
02:32:47,610 --> 02:32:49,380
一个震撼人心的故事
A striking story.

1318
02:32:50,450 --> 02:32:53,760
现在人们想知道故事的结局
Now the people want to know how the story ends.

1319
02:32:56,040 --> 02:32:58,390
只有一个出名的死亡才能令人满意
Only a famous death will do.

1320
02:33:00,210 --> 02:33:02,850
还有什么能比
And what could be more glorious

1321
02:33:03,130 --> 02:33:06,980
在竞技场上亲自挑战皇帝来的光荣呢
than to challenge the Emperor himself in the great arena?

1322
02:33:09,220 --> 02:33:12,360
- 你要和我决斗 - 为什么不
- You would fight me? - Why not?

1323
02:33:13,340 --> 02:33:15,490
你以为我害怕吗
Do you think I'm afraid?

1324
02:33:16,310 --> 02:33:19,430
我认为你一生人也在害怕
I think you have been afraid all your life.

1325
02:33:19,430 --> 02:33:23,240
不像无敌的马西墨斯 有谁从来不害怕
Unlike Maximus the Invincible, who knows no fear?

1326
02:33:28,900 --> 02:33:32,380
一个我认识的人曾经说过 "死亡向所有人微笑
I knew a man who once said, "Death smiles at us all.

1327
02:33:33,160 --> 02:33:35,760
人们所能做的就是还以微笑"
"All a man can do is smile back."

1328
02:33:37,450 --> 02:33:38,970
我在怀疑
I wonder,

1329
02:33:39,500 --> 02:33:42,390
你的朋友在面对死亡时也在微笑吗
did your friend smile at his own death?

1330
02:33:42,670 --> 02:33:44,270
你要知道
You must know.

1331
02:33:47,090 --> 02:33:48,980
他是你父亲
He was your father.

1332
02:33:52,760 --> 02:33:55,190
我知道 你爱我的父亲
You loved my father, I know,

1333
02:33:56,600 --> 02:33:58,200
但我也爱他
but so did I.

1334
02:33:59,720 --> 02:34:02,410
我们因此是兄弟 不是吗
That makes us brothers, doesn't it?

1335
02:34:04,940 --> 02:34:06,620
兄弟 对我微笑吧
Smile for me now, brother.

1336
02:34:12,530 --> 02:34:15,460
替他穿上盔甲 把伤口遮住
Strap on his armor. Conceal the wound.

1337
02:35:09,790 --> 02:35:11,850
成包围队形
Ring formation!

1338
02:37:03,530 --> 02:37:05,260
昆塔斯 剑
Quintus, sword.

1339
