把你的剑给我
Give me your sword.

1340
02:37:11,870 --> 02:37:13,980
剑 给我把剑
Sword! Give me a sword!

1341
02:37:15,380 --> 02:37:18,980
收剑入鞘 收剑入鞘
Sheathe your swords. Sheathe your swords!

1342
02:39:34,350 --> 02:39:36,960
马西墨斯
Maximus.

1343
02:39:42,940 --> 02:39:44,380
昆塔斯
Quintus.

1344
02:39:45,940 --> 02:39:47,500
还我的人自由
Free my men.

1345
02:39:48,780 --> 02:39:51,590
恢复格瑞克斯议员的职位
Senator Gracchus is to be reinstated.

1346
02:39:52,790 --> 02:39:54,970
罗马的共和是个梦想
There was a dream that was Rome.

1347
02:39:55,540 --> 02:39:57,510
