这些都是马可・奥勒留的心愿
These are the wishes of Marcus Aurelius.

1349
02:40:01,630 --> 02:40:03,730
释放囚犯 快去
Free the prisoners. Go!

1350
02:40:28,400 --> 02:40:29,840
马西墨斯
Maximus.

1351
02:40:31,620 --> 02:40:33,300
